This article describes the setup of an [[ACPI]] based docking stations and media bays.

== Installation ==
You need to activate the following kernel options:
{{Kernel||
Power management and ACPI options  --->
    [*] ACPI (Advanced Configuration and Power Interface) Support  --->
        [*] ACPI Support
            [*]   Dock
}}

== Usage ==
After the driver is loaded, for each docking station or media bay a directory <tt>/sys/devices/plattform/dock.0</tt>, <tt>.../dock.1</tt> et cetera will be created. The files and their informations can be used in scripts.

